    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tools for trimming or cutting back plants in gardening, flower arranging, and tree cultivation. There are various blade designs, which may incorporate two sharpened blades or one blade that meets a flat surface.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
